Package org.apache.paimon.manifest

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FileEntry
    Entry representing a file.
    ManifestCacheFilter
    Filter for manifest cache, this is used in AbstractFileStoreScan for improving cache utilization.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileEntry.Identifier
    The same FileEntry.Identifier indicates that the ManifestEntry refers to the same data file.
    IndexManifestEntry
    Manifest entry for index file.
    IndexManifestEntry.Identifier
    The IndexManifestEntry.Identifier of a IndexFileMeta.
    IndexManifestEntrySerializer
    A VersionedObjectSerializer for IndexManifestEntry.
    IndexManifestFile
    Index manifest file.
    IndexManifestFile.Factory
    Creator of IndexManifestFile.
    ManifestCommittable
    Manifest commit message.
    ManifestCommittableSerializer
    VersionedSerializer for ManifestCommittable.
    ManifestEntry
    Entry of a manifest file, representing an addition / deletion of a data file.
    ManifestEntrySerializer
    Serializer for ManifestEntry.
    ManifestFile
    This file includes several ManifestEntrys, representing the additional changes since last snapshot.
    ManifestFile.Factory
    Creator of ManifestFile.
    ManifestFileMeta
    Metadata of a manifest file.
    ManifestFileMetaSerializer
    Serializer for ManifestFileMeta.
    ManifestList
    This file includes several ManifestFileMeta, representing all data of the whole table at the corresponding snapshot.
    ManifestList.Factory
    Creator of ManifestList.
    PartitionEntry
    Entry representing a partition.
    SimpleFileEntry
    A simple FileEntry only contains identifier and min max key.
    SimpleFileEntrySerializer
    A VersionedObjectSerializer for SimpleFileEntry, only supports reading.
    WrappedManifestCommittable
    Manifest commit message.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FileKind
    Kind of a file.
